personalInfo.clubAffl: The Peninsula Club (Cornelius, North Carolina); River Run CC (Davidson, North Carolina)

tourBios.carHigh: 2013: Played on the eGolf Professional Tour, making 12 cuts in 20 events. Posted eight top-20 finishes, including a win at the Columbia Classic.
tourBios.otherCarHigh: While attending Fresno State University, made the all-region team and was also named 2007 team MVP...Was an Academic All-American in 2009...Made first team All-Western Athletic Conference in 2009.
tourBios.personal: If he weren't playing professional golf, he would be in the military special forces...Favorite athletes are Ken Griffey, Jr., and Wayne Chrebet...Has an identical twin brother...Favorite TV Shows are "The Office" and "The Walking Dead."...Cell phone ringtone is "Under Pressure" by Queen...Favorite pro teams are the San Diego Chargers, Los Angeles Dodgers and Los Angeles Lakers...The course he would most like to play is Augusta National.
